                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "N\u00b7m",
                    "stepConcepts": [
                        "66c394e5-9b27-4235-9105-6b2e0ba0b2b0"
                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "05e02eeaa04e4d6eae9eb",
                    "stepText": "Next, consider the resistance of the rod to rotation by determining its moment of inertia about its center. Identify the correct formula for the moment of inertia of a uniform rod rotating about its center.",
